sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant App as Mobile app
  participant API as API /v1/traces
  participant R as Redis stream
  participant W as Worker
  participant V as Valhalla
  participant PG as PostGIS

  Note over App: ride auto-detected<br/>(vehicle motion near route corridor)
  App->>App: buffer points in SQLite<br/>(offline-first, dead zones normal)
  App->>API: POST batch {batch_id, device_token,<br/>points[60], tags?}
  API->>API: auth + GPS sanity checks<br/>+ rate limit
  API->>PG: INSERT ... ON CONFLICT (batch_id) DO NOTHING
  API-->>App: 200 {ack: batch_id}
  Note over App,API: retry-safe: same batch twice = no dupes
  API->>R: XADD trace-events
  R->>W: consume on trace end (gap > 3 min)
  W->>W: trim to vehicle-motion window<br/>fuzz endpoints (drop first/last 100 m)<br/>rotate device id -> anon id
  W->>V: /trace_route (map matching)
  V-->>W: matched street segments + confidence
  W->>PG: store matched geometry + segments
  W->>PG: update route aggregate<br/>flag divergence (detour alert)
